Feature: This feature file contains scenarios for Call in Free CRM
Finished scenario

  Scenario: This scenario is to create call in CRM Application # CallCreation.feature:3
    Given User is on CRMHomePage                               # DealMapStepDefination.user_is_on_CRMHomePage()
    When User Navigates to New Call Page                       # CallCreationStepDefinition.User_Navigates_to_New_Call_Page()
    Then User enters the call details                          # CallCreationStepDefinition.user_enters_the_call_details(DataTable)
    And Extract the Task id                                    # CallCreationStepDefinition.extract_the_Task_id()
    And Extract the Case id                                    # CallCreationStepDefinition.extract_the_Case_id()
    And Extract the Deal id                                    # CallCreationStepDefinition.extract_the_Deal_id()
    And Click on Submit button                                 # CallCreationStepDefinition.click_on_Submit_button()
Feature: Contact Creation in FreeCRM
Finished scenario

  Scenario: This scenario is to create a contact in FreeCRM Application # ContactCreationFeature.feature:3
    Given User is on CRMHomePage                                        # DealMapStepDefination.user_is_on_CRMHomePage()
    When User Navigates to New Contacts Page                            # ContactCreationStepDefination.user_Navigates_to_New_Contacts_Page()
    Then User enters FirstName and LastName and Position details        # ContactCreationStepDefination.user_enters_FirstName_and_LastName_and_Position_details(DataTable)
    Then User clicks on Save button                                     # ContactCreationStepDefination.user_clicks_on_Save_button()
    Then Contact Created                                                # ContactCreationStepDefination.contact_Created()
